<Layout title="Selling an Investment Property with a Tenant in It: Complete Queensland Legal Guide for Owners and Agents | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Every legal step for selling a tenanted property in Queensland. Forms 9, 10 and 12 explained. Stage 2 reforms, entry rules, tenant consent, photography, open homes, settlement handover. For owners and agents.">

